injury.description: Aug 23: Falcons coach Raheem Morris said Friday that Landman is day-to-day due to a quad injury, Terrin Waack of the Falcons' official site reports.
Aug 13: Atlanta placed Burns (undisclosed) on its reserve-PUP list Tuesday, Aaron Wilson of KPRC 2 Houston reports.
Aug 21: Elliss was held out of Wednesday's practice due to a groin injury, William McFadden of the Falcons' official site reports.
